reviewText: I think some of the remedies are really effective but it is well known that Gary Null is a strong businessman before anything else.
I thought I was ordering a book.  But I made a mistake and overlooked the (VHS) marking.  I still haven't watched it.

This video is a very good look at a medical proublem that is very common and shows different views of different professionals and different treatments. If you are seeing a Dr. or thinking you might need to see a Dr. about joint pain and discomfort this video shows some options you might not have heard of- but may be suitable for you... I found this video very helpful and valuable...
